snippet.title: Techno Banter - Console Announcement Trailer | PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Techno Banter, the witty story of a club bouncer's misadventures will launch on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and Nintendo Switch this year!

You're the bouncer of the Green Door club, where every decision matters. Reject the unworthy of partying with clever retorts, explore a neon-lit city, and immerse yourself in the Berlin-like city's underground techno scene. The beat is pumping—are you in?
